---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, question, subject, trunc(_score, 3) as _score FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by _score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: _score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).question, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).subject, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score, Int64(3)) AS _score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, id, question, subject]                                                                                                                                                                                      |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@4 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@4 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@2 as id, answer@1 as answer, question@3 as question, subject@4 as subject, trunc(_score@0, 3) as _score]                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |         ProjectionExec: expr=[_score@1 as _score, answer@2 as answer, id@0 as id, question@3 as question, subject@4 as subject]                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |           HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1)], projection=[id@0, _score@1, answer@2, question@4, subject@5]                                                                                                                     |
|               |             CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |               AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[id@0 as id], aggr=[_score]                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                 RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([id@0], 3), input_partitions=3                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                   AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[id@0 as id], aggr=[_score]                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                     ProjectionExec: expr=[union_extract(json_get(key@0, id), int) as id, 1 - distance@1 as _score]                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                             CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                               S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): limit=100                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |             SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                 DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
